.Dd April 11, 2026
.Dt MOXY-HOOKS 5
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm moxy-hooks
.Nd hook event log format
.Sh DESCRIPTION
When
.Xr moxy 1
is invoked as a Claude Code hook handler
.Pq via Cm moxy hook ,
every hook event is appended to a per-session JSONL file under
.Pa $XDG_LOG_HOME/moxy/hooks/ .
.Pp
Each file is named
.Pa {session_id}.jsonl
where
.Ar session_id
is the Claude Code session UUID.
Each line is the raw JSON object sent by Claude Code on the hook's
stdin, with a
.Cm ts
field injected containing the UTC timestamp in RFC 3339 format.
.Sh HOOK EVENT TYPES
Claude Code sends several hook event types.
The
.Cm hook_event_name
field identifies the type.
Events currently logged:
.Bl -tag -width "PermissionRequest"
.It Cm PreToolUse
Fired before a tool executes.
Contains
.Cm tool_name
and
.Cm tool_input .
.Nm moxy
uses this to auto-allow moxin tools; the event is still logged
regardless of the permission decision.
.It Cm PermissionRequest
Fired when Claude Code is about to show an interactive permission
dialog to the user.
This indicates an
.Em agent pause :
the agent is blocked waiting for user input.
Contains
.Cm tool_name ,
.Cm tool_input ,
and
.Cm permission_suggestions .
.El
.Pp
Additional event types
.Pq e.g. PostToolUse, Stop, SessionStart
are logged if the hook is registered for them but are not currently
used by
.Nm moxy .
.Sh COMMON FIELDS
Every event contains at least:
.Bl -tag -width "permission_mode"
.It Cm ts
UTC timestamp in RFC 3339 format
.Pq injected by Nm moxy , not present in the original payload .
.It Cm hook_event_name
Event type string.
.It Cm session_id
Claude Code session UUID.
.It Cm tool_name
Tool that triggered the event
.Pq e.g. Dq Bash , Dq mcp__moxy__folio_read .
.It Cm tool_input
Object with the tool's input parameters.
.It Cm cwd
Working directory at the time of the event.
.It Cm permission_mode
Session permission tier
.Pq e.g. Dq default , Dq acceptEdits .
.El
.Pp
Events from subagents additionally contain:
.Bl -tag -width "agent_type"
.It Cm agent_id
Subagent identifier.
.It Cm agent_type
Subagent type
.Pq e.g. Dq Explore , Dq Plan .
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
A typical
.Cm PermissionRequest
entry:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
{"ts":"2026-04-11T18:25:15Z","session_id":"5d444361-...","hook_event_name":"PermissionRequest","tool_name":"mcp__moxy__folio-external_ls","tool_input":{"path":"/home/user/repos"},"cwd":"/home/user/project","permission_mode":"default"}
.Ed
.Pp
List all permission prompts from a session:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
jq -r 'select(.hook_event_name == "PermissionRequest") | .tool_name' \\
    ~/.local/log/moxy/hooks/{session_id}.jsonl
.Ed
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "$XDG_LOG_HOME/moxy/hooks/"
.It Pa $XDG_LOG_HOME/moxy/hooks/
Directory containing per-session hook event logs.
Defaults to
.Pa ~/.local/log/moxy/hooks/
when
.Ev XDG_LOG_HOME
is unset.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr moxy 1 ,
.Xr moxin 7
